Drag'n Download
===============
This is Chrome extension that make all the links downloadable by drag and drop.

INTRODUCTION

  Generally, dropping a link into the desktop/folder makes a shortcut to the
  link's target URL. It couldn't download the target content. This extension
  makes it possible.

